6.30	The_Ringworld_Throne	The Ringworld Throne	The Ringworld Throne is a novel by Larry Niven, first published in 1996. It is the direct sequel to his previous work The Ringworld Engineers (1980). He wrote it as a replacement after being unable to finish his contracted novel The Ghost Ships, the sequel to The Integral Trees and The Smoke Ring.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/42/RingworldThrone%28Niven%29.jpg/150px-RingworldThrone%28Niven%29.jpg
